name: MORAL EDUCATIONAL AND SOCIAL WELFARE SOCIETY MALEGAON DIST. NASHIK
briefDescription: Our Moral Educational and Social Welfare Society Malegaon Dist. Nashik (M.S) is working in the field of Education Since 1997. for welfare of the poor and needy people in Malegaon Dist. Nashik. Malegaon is the Second Largest Slum area of Maharashtra. Therefore here about 70 % of the people are below poverty line. and they cannot afford to give better education to their children. Therefore the aim of our society is to give free education to such children's
